taginfo / OSM Database (tag value enumeration)
-----------------------------------------------
For tag keys without an explicit value list in osm_tags.lua, cmd/build-dictionary
calls the taginfo API endpoint /api/4/key/values to enumerate popular values.
That endpoint returns statistics derived from the OpenStreetMap database.

OSM database data © OpenStreetMap contributors, licensed under the Open Database
License (ODbL) v1.0: https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/

The tag value strings themselves (e.g. "park", "river") are factual identifiers
from the OSM tagging schema; their use in osm_tags.csv is consistent with the
ODbL "Produced Work" provisions. The descriptions associated with those values
remain under CC-BY-SA 2.0 (see above).

